01:13.482 --> 01:16.413
Matt,
looking dapper today.

01:16.517 --> 01:18.896
Kate, you okay?
You look tired.

01:19.000 --> 01:20.896
[ Elevator bell dings ]

01:21.000 --> 01:26.896
